para_trans: Administrative Reforms, Structure and Procedures in the General Administration Department Regarding the change in the name of the subdivision
Government Decision No: SAPRA 1024 / P.S. 193 / Aastha-1
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,

The Government is approving the renaming of the subdivision "Administrative Reforms, Structure and Procedures" of the General Administration Division as "Administrative Innovation, Excellence and Good Governance."
The change in the name of the said subdivision shall come into force with immediate effect from the date of this order.
3. The decision of the Government of Maharashtra.
